EForm.Description: Form to store CSV files generated for Analytics reporting

Binding.Expression:
LET $url := EBMS_GET_BASE_URL(); LET $enterpriseName := ARRAY_LAST(SPLIT($url, "/")); LET $folderLocation := "\eformrecords\Analytics+Files\1\Analytics Files"; LET $instance := LEFT($url, FIND($enterpriseName, $url) - 1);
LET $rootfolder := IF( $instance == "https://uat-app.vendorpanel.com.au/", //uat "\\nimblexshareddrive.file.core.windows.net\nimblexapp\uatau-nimblex\attachments\",
$instance == "https://ebms.com.au/sql/", //legacy SQL "E:\Attachments\sql\",
$instance == "https://ebms.com.au/app/", //legacy APP "E:\Attachments\v4\",
$instance == "https://app.vendorpanel.com.au", //.au "\\prodausandy.file.core.windows.net\nimblex\prodau-nimblex\attachments\",
$instance == "https://app.vendorpanel.nz", //.nz "\\prodnzsandy.file.core.windows.net\nimblex\attachments\",
$instance == "https://app.vendorpanel.ca", //.ca "\\prodcasandy.file.core.windows.net\nimblex\attachments\",
$instance == "https://app.vendorpanel.net", //.net "\\prodgblsandy.file.core.windows.net\nimblex\attachments\",
"Not found" );
LET $folderPath := $rootfolder & $enterpriseName & $folderLocation;
RETURN IF( $rootfolder <> "Not found", $folderPath, "Folder path not found." )
